Japan denounced for blindly siding with U.S. 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, May 26 (KCNA) -- The Japanese government in a "written answer" approved at its recent cabinet meeting blindly sided with the U.S. It asserted that "the U.S. carefully selected the targets of cluster bombs in consideration of their nature and strove to prevent civilians from falling victim to them." It means that the U.S. use of cluster bombs does not pose an international problem as they were dropped technically in the Iraqi war.
 In this regard Rodong Sinmun today in a signed commentary says: This was nothing but Japan's shameful act of flattery and servile support for its master, the U.S. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The Japanese authorities are so obsessed with the idea of toeing the U.S. line that they took the lead in openly shielding the U.S. genocide, a target of the international community's condemnation. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 It is obvious that it is a bad habit of Japan to blindly support and flatter the U.S. as a servant does his master. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The point at issue is for what Japan behaves so. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The Japanese authorities are keen to whip the charriot of overseas military aggression under the U.S. umbrella of "anti-terrorism" strategy. Japan's act of supporting and shielding the U.S. use of weapons of mass destruction indicates that it will leave no means untried for overseas aggression as the U.S. does. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 But the Japanese authorities are well advised to bear in mind that if they continue acting blindly to the tune of the U.S. out of their senses, they will only meet a fatal fiasco.

Functions for friendship with DPRK held in Iran 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, May 26 (KCNA) -- Opening ceremonies of a week of Iran-DPRK friendship and a Korean book, photo and handicraft exhibition were held in Teheran on May 20.
 The general director for cooperation with foreign countries of the organization of culture and Islamic relations of Iran in a speech at the opening ceremony of the week of friendship said that the friendly DPRK government has long supported the just  stand of Iran, pointing out that the friendly ties between the two countries provided by President Kim Il Sung, the great leader of the Korean people, and Khamenei, leader of the Islamic revolution of Iran, are favorably developing. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Then participants saw with great attention photos showing the revolutionary exploits performed by Kim Il Sung and  Kim Jong Il, their famous works, photos and magazines dealing with successes made in socialist construction of the DPRK and handicrafts. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 They watched the Korean film "President of the Islamic Republic of Iran He Seyed Ali Khamenei's visit to our country".

South side's moves for confrontation with north flailed 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, May 26 (KCNA) -- The secretariat of the Committee for the Peaceful Reunification of the Fatherland on Sunday issued information bulletin no. 840 condemning the south side for its moves for confrontation with the north.
 Calling in question the fact that the national defence advisor of Chongwadae made remarks denying the system of the north a few days ago and then the foreign minister of South Korea told a silly story about the system, the bulletin noted: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 It is no other than a knockabout farce to block the voice of denunciation daily mounting at home and abroad after the south side's pro-U.S., flunkeyist and humiliating visit to the United States, shirk from the responsibility for leading the inter-Korean relations to a confrontation and tarnish the prestige of the DPRK. and it is another open act of anti-north confrontation. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 It cannot be interpreted as anything but another logic of a military way that the south side talked about "consideration of further steps" allegedly to find a peaceful solution of the "nuclear issue". &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 What is a way devoid of peace is only a non-peaceful way, a military way. And sanctions and blockade, a declaration of war against the north, are accompanied by a military way. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The south side can neither explain the grave reality with a few words nor avoid the responsibility for escalating the danger of a war on the Korean Peninsula and creating north-south confrontation. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The south side should not try to cover the truth with a poor excuse but recognize its wrongdoing and apologize to the nation. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The south side should know that if it resorts to the anti-north confrontation to lead the situation to extremes in cooperation with foreign forces in defiance of the repeated warnings of the north, the inter-Korean relations would be brought to naught and it would face an unimaginable disaster.

South Korean Solidarity of Peasants formed in S. Korea 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, May 26 (KCNA) -- An inaugural ceremony of the South Korean Solidarity of Peasants was held in Seoul on May 19 with the attendance of the South Korean Federation of Peasants Associations and 8 other peasants' organizations.
 The solidarity has been active after a preparatory committee for its inauguration was formed on March 24. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 A declaration issued at the inaugural ceremony referred to the fact that the South Korean agriculture is in the crisis of bankruptcy due to the flunkeyist and traitorous agricultural policy of the authorities. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Saying that the present agricultural crisis is the problem of all people, not a matter of peasants only, it stressed that the solidarity would play its role in catapulting the flagging agriculture.

Repeal of bills on "emergency" demanded 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, May 26 (KCNA) -- The Alliance of South Koreans in Japan for Democracy and Unification, the South Korean Youth League in Japan and other organizations under the South Korean Residents Association in Japan on May 15 released a joint statement demanding Japan repeal the bills allegedly intended to cope with "emergency" which causes Asian people's apprehension and worry about its conversion into a military power and overseas dispatch of the "self-defence forces".
 The joint statement referred to the dangerous nature of the bills, noting that the bills which passed through the house of representatives of the diet are war laws intended to attack somebody. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The Koreans in Japan still remember all forms of suppression and persecution by the Japanese authorities they experienced on the eve of the June 25 war more than 50 years ago and the on-going "anti-north campaign" in Japan reminds them of those times, it said, and stressed: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 What the Japanese government and diet should do is to respect the sovereignty of other nations and develop friendship with them and seek a peaceful solution to all issues through dialogue with the DPRK, not favoring the hostile policy of the United States.

Cinema and Radio Musical Company 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, May 26 (KCNA) -- The Cinema and Radio Musical Company is well known at home and abroad.
 It, formed in May Juche 47 (1958) for the first time in Korea, is based in the Pyongyang International Cinema House. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 It has developed into a powerful art troupe with competent creators and celebrated actors and actresses under the wise leadership of Kim Jong Il. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The company consists of a dual formation orchestra, light music ensemble, chorus, recording room, etc. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 When it was formed, the orchestra had only 28 musicians. But it has developed into a dual formation orchestra which can successfully play any kind of music. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Over last 3 decades, the light music ensemble with modern instruments has given 15,240 odd performances, inspiring the Korean people in their efforts for building a socialist economy and a great prosperous nation. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The recording room, equipped with up-to-date facilities, can record any music including cinema and radio music. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 It also accepts orders for cinema music from overseas Koreans.

Achievements in creation of cinema and radio music 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, May 26 (KCNA) -- Over the past 45 years since its foundation, the cinema and radio music company has created tens of thousands of pieces of music for feature films, documentary and scientific films, films for the children, tv literary and art works and radio broadcasting. They greatly contributed to the development of the country's art and the cultural and emotional life of the people.
 It has created 34,131 theme songs of films. Among them are such famous songs as "Song of Comradeship," "General's Family," "Song of Chollima Vanguard" and "We Will Live Long with Motherland" which are popular among the Korean people. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The company has also created more than 280 famous songs including "Don't Advance, Night of Pyongyang". &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The performance of the film music suite "Best is Our Country Led by the General" created by the company in 1996 was highly acclaimed by the audience. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The suite successfully reproduces the theme and other songs of the feature film "The Nation and Destiny" with orchestra and vocal solos, spiced with scenes of the film appearing on the back-drop of the stage. It is a unique form of art showing the pride of the Korean nation led by the peerlessly great man. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The songs created by the company are very popular among the people as they represent well the personalities of film characters and realistic themes.

Anecdote about Kim Jong Il 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, May 26 (KCNA) -- Kim Jong Il visited a newly built refined salt factory on May 9, Juche 87 (1998).
 Watching salt being produced at the factory, he said he was very happy to see snow-white refined salt. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 After tasting the salt, he said that its taste was very good and that his wish to provide the people with fine soy and salt had come true. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 He then solved all issues arising in updating the production processes and attaining a high and steady rate of production at the factory.

South side urged to keep faith
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, May 26 (KCNA) -- The behavior of the south side before and after the 5th meeting of the north-south committee for the promotion of economic cooperation arouses the north's apprehension as to whether the issues arising in implementing the June 15 joint declaration can be settled as required by the nation and in its interests. Rodong Sinmun today says this, commenting on the meeting which was opened here on may 23.
 The news analyst observes: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 At the meeting the head of the north side's delegation expressed deep concern over the fact that the south side in the "joint statement" published with the U.S. agreed with "further steps" which the world people interpreted as a blockade and military attack and worried about. If this actually happens to spark confrontation, the relations between the north and the south will be put at the lowest ebb and this will bring disasters to the south side, too, he added. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The south side, however, created complexities at the meeting and delayed the discussion, talking about "clarification." Who on earth is committed to clarify and apologize? &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 It was very disappointing that the south side behaved like a guilty party filing the suit first. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 What was alarming was that the south side did not bother to spread misinformation about the meeting, quoting an anonymous "high-ranking official of Chongwadae" even before the meeting came to an end. This clearly proves how perfidious and uneasy the south side was. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The south side should think over its improper acts of going against the idea of "by our nation itself," the basic spirit of the June 15 Joint Declaration.

Rodong Sinmun on calls of WPK
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, May 26 (KCNA) -- "Let Us Decisively Smash the U.S. Imperialists' Reckless Nuclear Racket and Moves for the Provocation of a New War with the Concerted Efforts of All the Fellow Countrymen Upholding the Slogan of Anti-U.S. Independence," one of the calls of the Central Committee of the  Workers' Party of Korea issued on the occasion of the 55th anniversary of the DPRK, is a very just and realistic militant slogan that conforms with the requirements of the prevailing situation and the desire of our nation, says Rodong Sinmun today in a signed article.
 Referring to the fact that the U.S. is seeking to achieve its criminal purpose with the policy of strength, aggravating confrontation and tension between the north and the south, the paper says: the prevailing situation requires the whole nation to smash the U.S. imperialists' moves against the DPRK with its concerted efforts under the slogan of anti-U.S. independence. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 It goes on: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The U.S. is intensifying blackmail on the DPRK, building up public opinion in a bid to isolate it politically. Lurking behind it is an ulterior intention to block the unity of the north and the south and justify a war of aggression on the north by convincing the international community that the north is a "nuclear criminal". &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The whole nation should unite close under the banner of "by our nation itself" as specified in the June 15 Joint Declaration. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 It is clear that confrontation on the Korean Peninsula comes between the whole Korean nation and the U.S. that is why all the fellow countrymen should conduct a vigorous anti-U.S., anti-war and peace drive to frustrate the U.S. imperialists' frantic nuclear racket and moves for the provocation of a new war with the firm independent stand that our nation should pool mind and efforts by itself and keep step with each other however hard the U.S. may threaten. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The whole nation in the north, the south and abroad should decisively smash the U.S. imperialists' reckless nuclear racket and moves for the provocation of a new war and speed up independent reunification with its concerted efforts, keeping in mind that anti-U.S. independence is the only way out of our nation and guarantees independent reunification.

KCNA assails U.S. psychological war against DPRK
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, May 26 (KCNA) -- Some media of the United States and South Korea recently spread a false report that scientists of the DPRK, who are now on their routine duty, sought "asylum." they have already reported without any ground that a man no longer alive sought "refuge."
 The DPRK announced that it was carrying out the work of processing spent fuel rods at the final stage. But they argued that this report was misinterpreted or not confirmed. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 They went to the lengths of telling a lie that the DPRK could not but come out to the Beijing talks as china kept the oil pipe blocked for three days. As this propaganda did not sound plausible they are these days bringing up again non-existent issues of the DPRK's "counterfeit money" and "drug trafficking," their trite tricks, in a bid to fool the world community. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 We have already clarified that the rumor about "exile of vice-department director Kil Jae Gyong" was a sheer lie. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The same is true of the recent report that "20 nuclear scientists of the DPRK sought asylum in the United States and other countries via China." &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 All the scientists of the DPRK are strong in revolutionary faith. They are devotedly working for the building of a great prosperous power. They can't do such a thing as they are ideologically ready to share the same destiny with their socialist homeland to the last. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 As far as the issue of reprocessing spent fuel rods is concerned, the DPRK made it clear on April 18 that it was successfully carrying out the work of reprocessing over 8,000 spent rods at the final stage. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 However, dishonest forces argued this was misinterpreted and not confirmed. Such allegation reminds one of the ostrich policy. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Their talk about "oil pipe" does not deserve even a passing note as it is a sheer fabrication invented to drive a wedge between the DPRK and China in the development of relations. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The same is true of "counterfeit money" and "drug trafficking". &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The above-mentioned practices are strictly prohibited under our socialist system. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 All the rumors spread by plot-breeders of the united states, styling itself the only superpower of the world, and South Korea are no more than a sinister trick to tarnish the image of the dignified DPRK, find a pretext to impose international sanctions and blockade on it and cause psychological unrest in its society in a bid to break the singlehearted unity of the DPRK. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The U.S. considers the psychological war very important in the U.S. hostile moves to isolate and stifle the DPRK over the "nuclear issue." &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The U.S. claims that it achieved "success" in the Iraqi war through a deceptive, hypocritical and cunning psychological war, something it could hardly gain by use of hi-tech weapons. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
It seeks to use this method against the DPRK. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 But such psychological war of the U.S. is not workable in the DPRK where the people are singleheartedly united, though it could work in the Iraqi war. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The U.S. should make a switchover in its hostile policy toward the DPRK, a key to removing the confrontation between the two countries over the nuclear issue, at an early date, far from trying to undermine our system through such war as foolish an act as sweeping the see with a broom.

Rodong Sinmun on community linked with same destiny
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, May 26 (KCNA) -- Rodong Sinmun today devotes one whole page to an editorial article titled "headquarters of revolution, single-hearted unity and socialism represent a community linked with the same destiny."
 The party, the army and the people of the DPRK will firmly defend the headquarters of the revolution, single-hearted unity and socialism, which represent the great community linked with the same destiny, and accomplish without fail the revolutionary cause of Juche pioneered in the forest of Mt. Paektu, the article says, and goes on: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The single-hearted unity serves as a source of the vitality of socialism. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The idea of the community linked with the same destiny is a great idea which has developed in depth the theory on the driving force of the revolution on a new higher plane. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The driving force of the revolution means an integral whole of the headquarters, the party, the army and the people. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Strengthening the driving force of the revolution, in essence, means closely rallying the party, the army and the people around the headquarters. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 As shown by the historical lesson, if the unity of the party, the army and the people around the headquarters of the revolution breaks, even strong military and economic power will prove ineffective and socialism collapse. This is the reason why the unity serves as a main source of the vitality of socialism. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The single-hearted unity serves as a solid political basis of socialism. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 This basis means a political force supporting socialism. in other words, it means the army and people closely rallied around the headquarters of the revolution. The army is the main player. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 It was the biggest weak point of the preceding theory that it failed to regard the army as an important political force of the revolution. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The single-hearted unity serves as a powerful engine for the development of the socialist society. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The engine of the socialist construction is built by the political and ideological might of the driving force of the revolution and the revolutionary enthusiasm and the creative zeal of the army and people united close behind the party and the leader. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 If the revolutionary army makes a breakthrough in the most difficult and important fields true to the idea and policy of the party and all the people fully display the revolutionary enthusiasm and creative zeal learning from the army's revolutionary spirit and militant trait, it is possible to vigorously accelerate socialist construction under any difficult circumstances. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 It is the immutable truth clearly proved in the most rigorous test of the revolution that single-hearted unity serves as a source of vitality of socialism. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Noting that the headquarters of the revolution is the core of the unity, the article goes on: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 If the single-hearted unity is the main source of the vitality of socialism, the headquarters of the revolution is the very core of the single-hearted unity. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The party, the army and the people form a harmonious whole united around the headquarters of the revolution. This is the main feature of the single-hearted unity. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The driving force of the revolution is a social and political organism in which the headquarters, the party, the army and the people are united as an organic body and its core is the headquarters of the revolution. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The destinies of the headquarters of the revolution, the party, the army and the people are inseparably linked with each other. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Only when the party, the army and the people are under the steermanship of the great headquarters, can they display invincible might and enjoy independent dignity and life. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Only when the headquarters of the revolution is absolutely trusted by the party, the army and the people, can it creditably fulfil its mission and role as a political leader steering the cause of socialism. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The party, the army and the people form an integral whole as they unanimously worship and follow the headquarters of the revolution as the sun taking care of their lives while the headquarters deeply trusts and leads them as revolutionary comrades with whom it shares the same destiny. This represents the single-hearted unity, the strongest of the unity. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The outstanding idea, experienced leadership and noble human trait of the great headquarters serve as a fundamental factor of the single-hearted unity. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 As flowers bloom thanks to the sun, the single-hearted unity has been achieved on this socialist land thanks to the headquarters of the revolution. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The single-hearted unity of the party, the army and the people around the headquarters of the revolution serves as the most powerful weapon of revolution. Any formidable imperialist enemy can be defeated and a great prosperous socialist power built even from debris only if there is the steel-strong single-hearted unity of the headquarters of the revolution, the party, the army and the people. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The glorious Korean revolution has achieved the single-hearted unity of the party, the army and the people and won one victory after another thanks to it as the revolution held President Kim Il Sung and leader Kim Jong Il in high esteem. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The article calls for fully demonstrating the might of this community linked with the same destiny. 
 The whole party and army and all the people should devotedly defend the headquarters of the revolution and strengthen the single-hearted unity. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Calling for frustrating the imperialists' moves to isolate and stifle the DPRK and devotedly defending the socialist homeland, the article underscores the need to consolidate the anti-imperialist military front, the lifeline of Korean-style socialism, to be a steel-strong fortress, remaining single-heartedly true to Kim Jong Il's Songun leadership.

Rodong Sinmun calls for devotedly defending headquarters of revolution
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, May 26 (KCNA) -- Rodong Sinmun today devotes its first whole page to an editorial article titled "the headquarters of the revolution, single-hearted unity and socialism are community united by destiny".
 We should make it the most important affair to devotedly defend the headquarters of the revolution and safeguard it politically and ideologically at the risk of our lives now that the imperialists are resorting to all sorts of sinister moves targeted at the headquarters of the revolution in a bid to break our single-hearted unity and stifle socialism of our style, the article says. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 We should become the comrades of faith, comrades of obligation who share destiny with the headquarters of the revolution to the last in any adversity and lay down their lives in defence of it, the article says, and goes on: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 All the developments in the international arena clearly show once again that any international laws and world public opinion can not check the high-handed and arbitrary practices of the imperialists nor defend sovereignty. It is the only way of reliably defending the socialist motherland to consolidate its self-reliant defence power under the banner of Songun. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 All the servicemen and people should always be ready to foil the undisguised aggressive moves of the imperialists, and they should wipe out the enemy at a single blow and settle all accounts with the U.S., if the enemy ignites a war of aggression.
